{"tid":717316,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉貼]牛市已死，熊市已經誕生。向27800進發，跌完後抽，再跌，完成熊一然後反彈。","createTime":"2018-06-26T02:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T11:18:11.000Z","uid":163916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"44cd92463941256f888f143f6f199a26b3034dc3","tid":717316,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:35:00.000Z","msg":"恆指自今年1月月線圖大陰燭，烏雲蓋頂。已經是熊市開始。<br />\n<br />\n不過在中段橫行，令人覺得仍然是牛市。已經橫行5個月。如果是牛市第三期是冇可能的事。今年股市横行，呃了很多人以為牛市未完，包括我都被騙，本來我早已睇淡。結果跌極唔落，以牛市未完，尚且去看那睇好的股評人。自我找按慰，但我有底線，跌破29129我就睇佢係熊市。不再信任何人講不是熊市，要信自己，歷史經驗知訴我，形勢已變，不宜再信那些唱好的人&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"85cccaf9f0a03326475bb7347704d76c7dd2d93e","tid":717316,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:38:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://blog.stheadline.com/article/detail/927457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.stheadline.com%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F927457&d=E7RA9VxKOw85D9Rl3au9hfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=0e982087\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.stheadline.com%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F927457&h=5f5ffd04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blog.stheadline.com/article/detail/927457</a>"},{"pid":"32871af0d3da5a2347524e0deff250b3644e3b70","tid":717316,"uid":24513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:51:31.000Z","msg":"見大頂後幾日已清倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7328716f1cab1d3ca9c40d4b89ed6474e9aaf759","tid":717316,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:10:07.000Z","msg":"冧冧冧！"},{"pid":"67b47fe44bd71e916786cc3ab02900cb894327b4","tid":717316,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:06:27.000Z","msg":"又500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adc60eaa4e56e4b72c97becf7a9a2802398ca59","tid":717316,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi